= Twisted =

Twisted is a networking engine written in Python, supporting numerous protocols.  It contains a web server, numerous chat clients, chat servers, mail servers, and more.

Twisted is made up of a number of sub-projects which can be accessed individually through the [wiki:TwistedProjects twisted projects index].

Twisted is available under the [http://www.opensource.org/licenses/mit-license.php MIT Free Software licence]. 

